      "title": "The RNA-binding protein HuR is essential for the B cell antibody response",
      "abstract": "The RNA-binding protein HuR post-transcriptionally regulates mRNA splicing. Turner and colleagues demonstrate that HuR serves a critical role in thymus-independent antigen responses by regulating the fate of genes related to B cell energy use."
